423. uxore excidit: “ is short a wife.” After his exclamations in 420 and 421, Burria quickly recovers his usual sang-froid.

424. It now remains for Simo to use the second string to his bow (see 165 ff). Now that Pampilus¹ has apparently been got away from Glucerium, Cremes may withdraw his ob- jections to the match.
